{"tid":1541961,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【文宣】仆街了，好多外國人以為香港贏左","createTime":"2019-09-04T17:02:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-06T13:57:41.000Z","uid":93536,"like":14,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"1d7f639ac980d576002476540ab717f41d86e0af","tid":1541961,"uid":93536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T17:02:57.000Z","msg":"六月已經好驚個柒婆講撤回散軍心，勢估唔到係今日講，<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">但屌你老母一切已經太遲喇！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n我相信香港人眼睛係雪亮的，唔會接受港共政府既空頭支票，但眼見好多國外既人都覺得香港贏左，國際戰線出現危機，所以我地一定要話返比佢地知，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">我地唔會忘記，唔會原諒，唔會接受呢個港共政府所做既一切暴行！</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n‪<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">HONGKONGERS ARE NOT DONE YET!‬<br />\n<br />\n‪- 3 Eyes lost‬<br />\n‪- 2 MTR terror attacks‬<br />\n‪- 8 deaths‬<br />\n‪- 100+ prosecutions‬<br />\n‪- 1,000+ arrests‬<br />\n‪- Countless injured‬<br />\n<br />\n‪With our tears and blood, only 1 of the 5 demands is PARTLY responded. Please continue to stand with HK, for FREEDOM &amp; JUSTICE!‬‬</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KUmvFm9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKUmvFm9.jpg&h=4bfa50b2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">驅逐共黨，光復香港！<br />\n五大訴求，缺一不可！</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"3e6180287870ad192fc533b8f1c723f15ab940db","tid":1541961,"uid":117906,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T17:03:44.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">撤LLM 對準政權</span></strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3E7OjKb.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3E7OjKb.gif&h=66b4ea40&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zNutjAi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzNutjAi.jpg&h=1817afe5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">得到黨媒認證</span></strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sELTeyX.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsELTeyX.png&h=0e8c0efe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">#Chinazi旗係一個符號，不斷向世界輸出反共思想！</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">#Chinazi 赤納粹</span></span></strong><br />\nChinazi就係China+Nazi。<br />\n赤=共產紅色恐怖, 納粹不解釋。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\"> 全民反共 對準政權！</span></span></strong><br />\n黑警、黨鐵，港共全部都係人民既敵人<br />\n而背後一直有一個終極大Boss中共<br />\n<br />\n呢一刻中共絕對係十個煲得兩個蓋，準備爆煲。<br />\n今日唔號召世界圍堵中共，更待何時？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">用#Chinazi黎connect全世界</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">1. Connect所有黃絲。</span></strong><br />\n殘酷既現實係，並唔係所有黃絲都支持勇武。但黃絲最驚就係共產黨打到黎，一於用反共connect呢班淺黃!<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">2. Connect部分中立/藍絲。</span></strong><br />\n中立/藍絲既上一輩，全部都係親身經歷過六四既年代，唔少甚至係大陸生活過。係大陸生活上所面對既不公義、中共點砌人生豬肉、佢地可能比我地感受更深。佢地唔會否認對共產黨既恐懼！一齊黎喚醒佢地對中共既不信任！<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">3. Connect全世界</span></strong><br />\nNazi既惡行到今時今日都依然係全世界既傷口，但佢地未必注意到係21世紀有個同Nazi不遑多讓既Chinazi！用#chinazi旗加海量文宣，話比佢地知我地既共同敵人係中共！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>目標：全香港市民都知到呢個符號！<br />\n請大家用各種創意方法令大家知道呢道Chinazi旗！<br />\n記住！存在即勝利！</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">雙手奉上</span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2019/09/02/9dojRG.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2019%2F09%2F02%2F9dojRG.png&h=baf47345&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JXMrzU3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJXMrzU3.jpg&h=4fd76574&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uZFWW8o.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuZFWW8o.jpg&h=4196affc&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"dc6a80d7f965e8a55bc107e817142d15372db7d5","tid":1541961,"uid":93536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T17:03:54.000Z","msg":"自推十年，一齊Tweet爆佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"10ff4ce2dce2bee9c7cddf2091f850e8c26177d1","tid":1541961,"uid":93536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T17:04:42.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">香港人權民主法案必須通過！</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"16bb605d0975800ce764e7abe283f7bb8e9e2477","tid":1541961,"uid":93536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T17:04:52.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">香港人權民主法案必須通過！</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"0eae54522140e4aa6ff844fe4cf2e89f070f3a3e","tid":1541961,"uid":93536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T17:05:03.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">香港人權民主法案必須通過！</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"aa71972dfd8e8231f90c80df7b41c2d79e88dbc9","tid":1541961,"uid":93536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T17:05:20.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">香港人權民主法案必須通過！</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"fa8bdd148e1c1ae3272ca89ead58c7b5fb2b48a5","tid":1541961,"uid":93536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T17:05:31.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">香港人權民主法案必須通過！</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"4907d4af94394877223e255103d3d382d055d8bf","tid":154